Class ResidentList

java.lang.Object
model.ResidentList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ResidentList extends Object implements Serializable
A class that represents a list of residents. Provides functionality for adding, removing, and retrieving residents, as well as calculating the total amount of personal points in the list.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Yuliia Iliienko
